into the crowd.

97
00:05:47,613 --> 00:05:49,603
Good evening. We're BLAST.

98
00:05:53,923 --> 00:05:55,553
Damn it, it's begun!

99
00:05:55,653 --> 00:05:58,353
Hey, I can hear it.
They sure play loud!

100
00:05:58,463 --> 00:05:59,793
I wanna go in!

101
