talks about the Demon Lord

125
00:06:51,083 --> 00:06:52,483
is not because she's matured,

126
00:06:52,483 --> 00:06:54,643
but because she's switched over
to the religion of BLAST.

127
00:06:54,913 --> 00:06:56,143
Bottom line, she needs something
to depend on.

128
00:06:57,113 --> 00:06:58,853
Well, at least she's more positive
about things now

129
00:06:58,853 --> 00:07:01,553
than back when she'd blame everything
on the Demon Lord.

130
00:07:02,453 --> 00:07:04,283
Besides, BLAST is really cool.

131
00:07:04,693 --> 00:07:06,823
