than live with me.

238
00:12:10,263 --> 00:12:11,633
It all makes sense.

239
00:12:13,533 --> 00:12:18,023
But if that's the case...
she no longer needs me.

240
00:12:19,403 --> 00:12:24,473
It's such a shame, Miss Hachiko.
After making all this food.

241
00:12:24,743 --> 00:12:25,473
Huh?

242
00:12:26,383 --> 00:12:28,243
Oh, right!

243
00:12:28,353 --> 00:12:29,513
It can't be helped,
given the circumstances.

244
00:12:29,513 --> 00:12:32,353
Don't feel pressured into eating more
than you want, Misato.

245
00:12:32,453 --> 00:12:35,183
But everything's so delicious.
It would be hard not to overeat.

246
00:12:35,553 --> 00:12:39,783
You're a very good cook,
Miss Hachiko. I'm impressed.

247
00:12:42,063 --> 00:12:44,793
Misato is such a nice girl.

248
00:12:45,803 --> 00:12:48,233
She is so much in love with Nana,

249
00:12:48,233 --> 00:12:50,933
yet will never show hostile sentiments
to those around her.

250
00:12:51,773 --> 00:12:54,433
And she was honestly happy
about Nana and Ren.

251
00:12:55,213 --> 00:12:57,113
She's a really cute, good girl.

252
00:12:57,873 --> 00:13:01,283
Which exhausts me all the more
with my tendency to be cynical.

253
00:13:02,613 --> 00:13:05,713
I wonder if we can get along
for a full month.

254
00:13:07,183 --> 00:13:09,623
